1. Insurance companies, branches of non-life insurance companies and mutuals providing microinsurance products shall have the following rights:

Request insurance companies, branches of non-life insurance companies and mutuals providing microinsurance products to return security deposit or collateral under contractual terms and conditions of insurance agent agreements;
dd) Exercise other rights in accordance with law.
